  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Toast the bread slices until lightly browned, about 5 minutes per side.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the smoked paprika, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Brush the toasted bread slices with the olive oil and sprinkle with the spice mixture.",
    "Drizzle the red wine vinegar over the bread slices and sprinkle with thyme.",
    "Top each bread slice with grated cheddar cheese.",
    "Place the bread slices under the broiler for 1-2 minutes, until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for a few minutes before serving.",
    "Serve warm, garnished with additional thyme if desired."
  ],
